Name: Cartridge Monsters
About the game: You are the heir to the Capture Clan. Complete quests to save the towns. Catch new monsters, level up and save the world from the evil one called Django. There are over 65 Unique Monsters in the game. So, put together the strongest team by discovering the strengths and weaknesses of your monsters and leveling up their power! Key Features: Developed from the ground up for VR Original Soundtrack Control Monsters with your Voice Story driven with Side Quests (Hours of Gameplay) Variety of monsters and Hidden Rare Monsters Level up and Unlocking new Skills Exploring Dungeons and Collecting Loot Over 65 Unique Monsters!
